------------------------------------------------------------------------
WHAT THIS PACKAGE IS
------------------------------------------------------------------------

This directory repackages 全宋體 (distributed by the author as seven
whole TTF files, deps/fonts/FSung-*.ttf in the parent repository) into
256-codepoint WOFF2 slices with a generated CSS file, for use as a
self-hosted webfont on the 部件檢索 project. No glyphs were modified;
only the file format, chunking, and packaging were changed. The build
script (../build-wfg-fsung.py) documents exactly how the slices were
produced and can regenerate them from the original TTF files.

Because this differs in character from the other permissively-licensed
fonts distributed under the sibling `free-fonts` project's packages,
this package is kept unpublished (not pushed to npm, not listed in
`free-fonts`' README/index.html) unless and until the non-commercial
scope has been explicitly reconciled with that project's distribution
model.
